    "Bench (Patil et al., 2023) collects 1,716 machine learning APIs from 3 public model hubs.",
    "ToolBench (Qin et al., 2023) provides a high-quality dataset containing 16,464 real-world APIs collected from RapidAPI Hub.",
    "ToolAlpaca (Tang et al., 2023) uses real-world APIs similar to ToolBench, with 3,938 instances.",
